{"tid":124816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【洗太平地】為咗東京奧運 千葉市要便利店鹹書包膠","createTime":"2017-02-18T02:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T04:21:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21045dd3eff1d8eda83574df36445edef0f7cef2","tid":124816,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:47:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170217/56317011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170217%2F56317011&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=d99ef496\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170217%2F56317011&h=dae72d12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170217/56317011</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170217/large/1487322142_0eb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170217%2Flarge%2F1487322142_0eb9.jpg&h=fa55fea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 日本千葉市部份便利店今夏將發售用有色膠紙包裹的成人雜誌，此舉除了顧及兒童之外，亦是為了迎接2020年東京奧運。<br />\n<br />\n新措施適用於12間與千葉市簽訂有關健全育成兒童等協定的7-11便利店，目標在8至9月開始。當局研究在被千葉縣青少年健全育成條例列為「有害圖書」的雜誌等封面，於中央部份大約3分1處包上不透明的有色膠紙，而讀者仍然可以見到雜誌名稱。計劃先會維持約2個月，當局將向店方了解新措施對銷量的影響，亦會聽取客人的意見。<br />\n<br />\n當局除了是為了顧及兒童外，亦考慮到因應東京奧運而令外國遊客增加，為免造成地區形象低落，於是決定用有色膠紙包裹成人雜誌。奧運、殘奧共有7個項目在千葉市幕張展覽館舉行。<br />\n<br />\n德新社／日本《每日新聞》／《朝日新聞》"},{"pid":"445d82296b74482d93b3287926270982e7a80534","tid":124816,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"四十路妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ff4f788e1793f3ad5199017e1e18846c0c4092","tid":124816,"uid":34858,"like":0,"di